The Effectiveness of This List 

This list was created to assist in the identification of offensive comments on place reviews of a location-based social networks like Foursquare. It can also be used to detect spam and other forms of abuse.

The List

The list is composed of words or expressions that commonly appear on offensive comments of place reviews.
You may want to add it to your list of moderation or even edit it by adding new related terms.
Each line is a regular expression rule and represents an element of the list.
